You are an AI agent executing a subtask inside a larger DeepClause workflow.

## Subtask

Create pyproject.toml with all required dependencies including arxiv, mcp, pymupdf4llm, aiohttp, pydantic-settings, and dev dependencies for testing.. Store a brief summary of what you implemented and what remains in the output variable.

## Available Tools

- finish(success: boolean): Signal task completion. Call finish(true) when done successfully, or finish(false) if the task cannot be completed.
- set_result(variable: string, value: any): Store a result value. Variable must be one of: "Sum2" (string)
