[log] bash[309] stdout     """Build the arXiv search query with field specifiers and optional category filter.
[log] bash[309] stdout     If the query does not already start with a field specifier, wrap it with `all:`
[log] bash[309] stdout     so that arXiv searches across all fields, improving relevance.  If categories
[log] bash[309] stdout     are provided, append a `cat:` filter for each category.
[log] bash[309] stdout     """
